### âœ… How to Use in Your Components

1. **Import the Component*: îˆƒAt the top of your `.razor` file, ad:îˆ„îˆ†

   ```razor
   @using Star.Shared.Components
   ```

îˆ„îˆ†

2. **Implement the Loader*: îˆƒWithin your component, use the `StarLoader` component conditionally based on your loading stae:îˆ„îˆ†

   ```razor
